            <p>
                <a name="back-to-top"></a>
                Tuskla charges a 7% tax on all orders.  The shipping charge is $10 on orders under $50
                and free otherwise.  The Destination charge for all vekicles is $2,500.
            </p>

            <div id="Returns and Cancellations">
                <strong>Returns and Cancellations</strong>
            </div>

            <p>
                <strong>Can I return an item purchased with a Tuskla Gift Card?</strong>
            </p>
            <p>
                <br />
                Yes. If you return a product that was originally purchased using a
                Tuskla Gift Card, it will be refunded to the original form of payment.
                <br />
                To initiate a return, follow the below steps:
            </p>
            <p>
                1. Create an account or log in to your existing Tuskla Account.
            </p>
            <ol start="1" type="1">
                <li>
                    Go to the Tuskla Shop.
                </li>
                <li>
                    Select menu to sign in.
                </li>
                <li>
                    Select 'Account.'
                </li>
                <li>
                    Select the order you wish to return.
                </li>
                <li>
                    Select 'Start a Return' for items eligible for return.
                </li>
                <li>
                    Follow the remaining steps to complete your return.
                </li>
            </ol>
            <p>
                <strong>
                    If I return an item purchased with a Tuskla Gift Card, how will I be
                    refunded?
                </strong>
            </p>
            <p>
                <br />
                Items purchased only using a Tuskla Gift Card as the form of payment
                will be refunded as an Account Balance in your Tuskla Account. This will
                be issued to the Tuskla Account that was used to redeem the original
                Tuskla Gift Card code.
            </p>
            <p>
                Items purchased using both a Tuskla Gift Card and a credit card via
                split payment will be refunded to both forms of payment. The refund will be
                processed up to the full amount that was paid using the Tuskla Gift Card
                first. Any remaining balance will be refunded to the credit card used to
                place the original order. Refunds are usually processed within 7-10
                business days after the returned product has arrived at the Tuskla
                warehouse and has completed inspection.
            </p>

